Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.44,Default,Bri,0,0,0,,A call from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.23,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,作戦本部　私だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.70,Default,Oli,0,0,0,,Mission headquarters? It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.07,Default,Oli,0,0,0,,What's the status over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.95,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっちはどうなっている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.28,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,閣下　中央司令部が…
